\par }{\cf1\insrsid13390822 Four hundred or five hundred chains surrounding the bandstand, where people can sit all night, under the heavens. In winter, such as it is in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname State}}California
{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, outdoor heating can be installed.}{\insrsid13390822  
\par }{\cf1\insrsid13390822 Around this, the great pedestrian treadway. On this, real people actually working!}{\insrsid13390822  
\par }{\cf1\insrsid13390822 And around them, in turn, the shops, the theatre.}{\insrsid13390822  
\par }{\cf1\insrsid13390822 Underneath: parking. Or the next block over, hidden, for God\rquote s sake, behind bushes and trees.}{\insrsid13390822  
