rtant element that remain constant is the center, the conversation pit, the plaza walk - around concourse where people }{\i\cf1\insrsid13390822 know}{\cf1\insrsid13390822 
, are absolutely sure if they bother to go, they will se someone they knew from junior high school, college or some neighborhood area.}{\insrsid13390822  \line }{\cf1\insrsid13390822 Let\rquote 
s start with one plaza such as this, and build more. Needless to say, the ones that follow must not duplicate the first in texture or color or sense of drama.}{\insrsid13390822  \line }{\cf1\insrsid13390822 
Just as in the great cities of the world, there is only one Eiffel Tower for Paris, one Tower of London, one St. Peter\rquote 
s for Rome, so, on a lesser level, each plaza in all 80 lost and needful Los Angeles small town should in some way strike individual chords of the backgrounds they arise from. In {\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname place}}West Hollywood{\*\xmlclose}
, of course, you would let the crazy fine {\*\xmlopen\xmlns1{\factoidname place}}Greenwich Village{\*\xmlclose} spirit that runs wild there work your design for you. }{\insrsid13390822 
